metadata.name: Crypto Planets #1
metadata.description: Crypto Planets, 500 Planet's wandering in space, we will be planting a tree for every planet sold to support saving your planet! and putting 50% of all future royalties from this project to good cause, planting tree's, cleaning the ocean, adoption centers and more Did you know that planting one oak tree brings in more insect and bird species than an entire yard of plants?, imagine what 500 trees can do!
